## Problem Statement
Ted loves prime numbers and plays a game called legendary with his girlfriend Robin. Ted writes a number N on a table in the form of P1A1 * P2A2 * ……….. * PnAn, where P1, P2, ………, Pn are distinct prime numbers and A1, A2, ………, An are their corresponding powers. Robin needs to find the sum of all the numbers which are less than or equal to N and also contain all the primes whose minimum power in the number is given by an array B.

